        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The tip of an oar-like limb specialized for swimming becomes a spiny eurypterid when activated. It can be called upon once a week for up to 24 hours. The eurypterid can serve as a mount for a creature one size smaller than it or smaller, and when it does, it confers the ability to breathe both air and water upon its rider.",
