        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A minuscule insect preserved in fossilized tree sap, this fragment becomes a giant mosquito when activated. It can be called upon once per day for up to 10 minutes. The fossil mosquito can't afflict anyone with septic malaria. If the mosquito uses Blood Drain, it doesn't gain temporary Hit Points, but instead collects blood from the victim. The blood stays within the mosquito indefinitely and stays fresh while it does. If the mosquito uses Blood Drain again, any blood from before that use is lost.",
        "type": "stat_block"
      },
